iceFlake
Open Compute Platform

Vibhaj Rajan <vibhaj8@gmail.com>

Subsystems
	DB:		Database
	IO:		Input/Output
	NS:		Name Service
	RT:		Runtime
	JN:		Journal
	FN:		Callback
	SI:		Smart Interface
	UI:		User Interface

Definitions
	Service: 	Functions with single argument - a Map: an array of key-value pairs, 
				returning a Map with all results
				Return Map must contain Status Keys ( 'valid', 'msg', 'details' )
	Message:	Service Invocation Definition ( SID ) for Service Runtime Invocation ( SRI )
	Workflow:	Array of Messages for Service Flow Orchestration ( SFO )
	Navigator:	String Encoding for Workflow ( SEW )  
	State:		Instance State Registry
	Config:		Instance Configuration Registry

Inspirations:
	DB:		Codefest 2010 Website ( JR Harshath )
	IO:		Yahoo! Buzz
	NS:		TPR Executive
	RT:		GSoC 2011 DSpace RESTClient
	JN:		Yahoo! Graph
	FN:		Yahoo! Buzz
	SI:		FireSpark
	UI:		Orbitnote

